{"tid":1422874,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠猛於虎","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:10.000Z","uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab10681ad4688f2c2622b8dfbd692be9ea6befc","tid":1422874,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"孔子過香港側。有手足哭於天耀者而哀。夫子式而聽之。使子路問之，曰：「子之哭也，壹似重有憂者。」而曰：「然，昔者天琦囚於激進，之鋒又囚焉，今吾手足又囚焉。」夫子曰：「何為不去也？」曰：「無左膠。」夫子曰：「小子識之，左膠猛於虎也。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">子曰：左膠或有利，然將在外，軍令有所不受</span></span>"},{"pid":"c018ce6b33430d68088bea931b2c8962b26936cf","tid":1422874,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:17:29.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36550477739fd9e7237fd323e4501782ea5a7059","tid":1422874,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a9674e2b4e7afea2a9f143d096f87596b9ecd460","tid":1422874,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"幾時都啱用，溫柔地抗爭，不流血的革命"}]}